org.mundo.rt
Interface IReceiver

All Known Implementing Classes:
ContentBroker, FilteredBroker, FilteredSet, MundoInputStream, MundoObjectInputStream, ObjectAdapter, P2PTopicBroker, ResultSet, Session
public interface IReceiver

Classes that want to receive messages have to implement the IReceiver interface. The reference to a receiver object is usually specified when creating subscriptions.
